    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="article"&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;div&gt;
        This is a special showcase due to the fact that
       &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;this site which you are looking at is actually the showcase itself&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
       &lt;br&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
        I.e. the full documentation site of the publishing bot, enriched with images, videos and detailed content is edited in Evernote and published via the publishing bot.
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
       &lt;br&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
        Actually, we are following the principle &amp;lsquo;eat your own dogfood&amp;rsquo; within Cloudburo, i.e. we are using our own product for content publishing. This allows us to constantly fine-tune the offering and improve its usability and efficiency.
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
       &lt;br&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
        Stroll around on our site and check out some pages to get a feeling how a full-fledged site could look like. Best is to start on the
       &lt;a href="https://curation.cloudburo.net/"&gt;home page&lt;/a&gt;, which gives you a detailed overview.
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
       &lt;br&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
       &lt;div&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
          More
         &lt;a href="https://curation.cloudburo.net/tags/showcase.html"&gt;Cloudburo Publishing Bot Showcases&lt;/a&gt;.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
         &lt;br&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
       &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
       &lt;span style="font-size: 11px;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;This blog entry was fully produced within Evernote and published using the &lt;a href="https://publishingbot.cloudburo.net"&gt;Cloudburo Publishing Bot&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
